  fhir:description [ fhir:v "IMMZ.D2.DT.TBE.FSME-Immun\nFSME-Immun schedule\n(In areas where the disease is highly endemic, implying that there is a high individual risk of infection, WHO recommends that vaccination be offered to all age groups, including children)"] ; # 
